Subject: [PATCH 176/241] x86/mm: Use __flush_tlb_one() for kernel memory
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

CVE-2017-5754

__flush_tlb_single() is for user mappings, __flush_tlb_one() for
kernel mappings.

